Karkern 53 puller of Bushido Clan <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukocherlightningfists.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kocher Lightningfists</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 13<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/4/02 11:33:24 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=306.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Resists changes and what it means to the average monk</span><hr size=1> Heh, I was getting hit for full 300's with 250+ FR by fire wurms and 300 b cold wurms with over 300 cr while doing Lend tonight.  Great change. *cough* <p>Sensei Kocher Lightningfists<BR>
